<title>BELGIUM: EU clears Boeing merger in principle - source.</title>
<headline>EU clears Boeing merger in principle - source.</headline>
<dateline>BRUSSELS 1997-07-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>The European Commission on Wednesday gave preliminary approval to a planned $15 billion merger between Boeing Co and McDonnell Douglas, an EU source said.</p>
<p>&quot;One Commissioner told me that there was an agreement in principle and that the formal decision will be taken next week,&quot; the source said.  </p>
<p>EU Competition Commissioner Karel van Miert was due to announce the Commission's decision at a news conference at 1000 GMT.</p>
